The Kardashians take over Tokyo.

Before the arrival of the baby Khloe Kardashian the Keeping up The star of Kardashhians decided to make a trip of sisters to Tokyo with Kim Kardashian and Kourtney Kardashian . Since arriving in Tokyo earlier this week, the trio has been coming out in some pretty fierce and futuristic ensembles.

"I'm going to publish something in Tokyo fashion very fast since it's 5 in the morning and I can not sleep," Kim tweeted. Wednesday. "All season 7 of Yeezy." He then shared pictures of his night in Tokyo on Tuesday wearing silver spandex.

"Night in Tokyo #SilverSurfer," Kim tweeted along with the photos.
